&lt;p&gt;    $ git pull &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/nwbirnie/cxf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/nwbirnie/cxf&lt;/a&gt; cxf6795&lt;/p&gt;

